name: White Widow
description:
Citrus flower 
woody soul
dry land
honeydew leaf flower sun.
Spirit of the forest
rebelliousness lives;
white widow
evening perfume
rest in daylight
colors the euphoria,
sweet and smooth
button 
of nostalgia.
